{"tid":196511,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"好多老人家持老賣老，迫年青人讓座","createTime":"2017-04-11T11:08:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T15:42:18.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"55a3e058d9a34a1d6d1716575dd9939aec042aec","tid":196511,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T11:08:30.000Z","msg":"明明許多老人家大把時間，日日無野do<br />\n仲要係繁忙時間搭車<br />\n這樣都算<br />\n還要迫年青人讓座<br />\n有些年青人工作太累，回家時在地鐵上睡著<br />\n這些老而不還拍醒他們，迫他們讓座<br />\n<br />\n這些老人家是民建聯忠實支持者，他們忠誠地支持獅子山下精神<br />\n他們很多是大中華愛國人仕，但他們又居住香港，當年更是受盡港英政府的好處，吃英國的奶水大，但心繫中國<br />\n現在更持老賣老，而且打壓下一代，是港共政府支持者，大中華人仕"},{"pid":"7f4e49c899364def288ebabd264bbfe4744f5fc5","tid":196511,"uid":61431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T11:09:54.000Z","msg":"2蚊撚"},{"pid":"94a086f3363b4ef29c7397050c5d88d15a965753","tid":196511,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T11:55:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9476199943a3d00c2d88d0b8625f90c023784b1c","tid":196511,"uid":103318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T12:08:26.000Z","msg":"無是咁的，0分"},{"pid":"3350a49053f695eb16b4dd756f44274c8820a8b7","tid":196511,"uid":89392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T12:10:45.000Z","msg":"搭巴士坐上層咪唔洗煩"},{"pid":"f1eaaf0bd62bcc11e94034269698d12933553e49","tid":196511,"uid":1554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T12:11:13.000Z","msg":"絕對唔讓<br />\n啲廢老拍我片囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84173be00d744e2901acf7b3bbaf38c427776ce2","tid":196511,"uid":9215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T12:18:45.000Z","msg":"恃"},{"pid":"903051329c66f5d8951a69111a5856875462510e","tid":196511,"uid":55990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:11:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"620f45fe1ed1c34cc887ed45b2717c55566bacc1","tid":196511,"uid":1554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:42:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>絕對唔讓<br />\n啲廢老拍我片囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n求你都唔讓???<br />\n你守護自己權力嘅力度眞強呀</blockquote><br />\n講緊恃老賣老就絕對唔讓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果嗰個老人家真係有需要嘅就會讓<br />\n例如你見到佢行路真係好慢行動不便<br />\n<br />\n但講蝗語嘅幾老都唔讓"}]}